{
  "stem": "5740.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he thought that in Warsaw he'd be able to have some, you know, some connection to somebody who can-- who can verify that my father hasn't done anything, that he is-- that he is not guilty of nothing.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because then we knew that they-- they will-- to carry-- take him to Kartuz-Bereza.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Kartuz-Bereza was the first concentration camp in Poland.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They used to take the really like communist, and people which were-- they-- they used to-- to treat the people there like in-- in labor camps.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Polish of-- of Polish police.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Polish--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes-- camp.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's why my-- my-- my brother couldn't get an audition to anybody of those big-- big people, like rich [NON-ENGLISH] at that time, or whoever was at the-- at the top of the government.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they promised him that he will be able to talk to them on Monday.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But in the meantime, they took my father away into the-- with-- with the police, which were pretty nice to him.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "My brother said that they were cracking jokes even.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the police told me then-- told us or told me-- that my father put on the tallit when he was close to Bereza.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he was praying.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then he complained that he had got-- got pains in his chest.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But they wouldn't believe him.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they took him down from the Kartuz-Bereza train-- in Kartuz-Bereza, from the train, to a buggy and horse.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in that buggy and horse, he was supposed to reach Kartuz-Bereza.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But when they got to Kartuz-Bereza, they tried to push him-- to take him down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He-- he was dead already.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He never reached Kartuz-Bereza.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] [CRYING] He must have been-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
